plasma6-jarvis (0.1.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * LLM token streaming via SSE — real-time response display
  * Sentence-based TTS pipeline — speaks first sentence while LLM generates
  * Piper TTS sentence-queue architecture
  * Native compilation optimizations (-march=native -O3)
  * New streamingResponse Q_PROPERTY for QML
  * Improved stop behavior — clears entire TTS queue instantly

